title: 151 Liquid Jewellery Cleaner with Basket for Silver, Gold and Diamonds, 145ml
features: VERSATILE CLEANING: Effectively cleans and restores shine to gold, silver, and diamond jewellery in one simple solution
EASY TO USE: Includes a convenient basket for safe submersion and cleaning of delicate jewellery pieces
GENEROUS SIZE: 145ml bottle provides multiple cleaning sessions for your precious jewellery collection
QUICK RESULTS: Removes tarnish, dirt, and buildup to restore the original lustre of your precious items
PROTECTIVE FORMULA: Gentle yet effective cleaning solution that maintains the integrity of your valuable jewellery
description: Product Description Keep your precious jewellery sparkling with this convenient 151 Liquid Jewellery Cleaner. The 145ml solution comes with a handy basket, making it simple to clean multiple pieces at once. Suitable for use on silver, gold, and diamonds, this versatile cleaner helps restore shine and brilliance to your favourite pieces. The specially formulated solution works effectively to remove daily buildup and tarnish, revealing your jewellery's natural lustre. The included basket allows for safe, controlled cleaning while protecting delicate items. Perfect for maintaining both costume and fine jewellery at home, this cleaner offers a practical solution for keeping your treasured pieces looking their best. Regular use helps maintain the appearance of your jewellery collection, ensuring your pieces continue to sparkle and shine. Ingredients Cleaning Solution For Jewellery
